## Agent trigger testing

The agent has three trigger modes with different permissions:

| Trigger | `stop_bot` allowed | When used |
|---|---|---|
| `scheduled` | ❌ blocked | `RunAgentConsultationJob` every 5 min |
| `manual` | ✅ allowed | User clicks "Consultar Agente" |
| `sl_tp_alert` | ✅ allowed | `RunAgentAlertJob` on SL/TP price hit |

When testing agent behavior, pass the trigger to `AgentOrchestrator::consult($bot, $trigger, $alertContext)`.

