## Feature test — Web controller

Use `actingAs($user)`. Bots and accounts require ownership checks (403).

```php
class MyControllerTest extends TestCase
{
    use RefreshDatabase;

    public function test_index_renders_page(): void
    {
        $user = User::factory()->create();

        $this->actingAs($user)
             ->get(route('my-route'))
             ->assertInertia(fn ($p) => $p->component('MyPage'));
    }

    public function test_other_user_is_forbidden(): void
    {
        $owner = User::factory()->create();
        $other = User::factory()->create();
        $bot   = Bot::factory()->create(['user_id' => $owner->id]);

        $this->actingAs($other)
             ->get(route('bots.show', $bot))
             ->assertForbidden();
    }
}
```

