## Feature test — API controller

Auth via `X-API-Key` header (auto-generated on `User::factory()->create()`).

```php
class MyApiControllerTest extends TestCase
{
    use RefreshDatabase;

    private function headers(User $user): array
    {
        return ['X-API-Key' => $user->api_key];
    }

    public function test_requires_api_key(): void
    {
        $this->getJson('/api/v1/my-endpoint')->assertUnauthorized();
    }

    public function test_returns_data(): void
    {
        $user = User::factory()->create();

        $this->getJson('/api/v1/my-endpoint', $this->headers($user))
             ->assertOk()
             ->assertJsonStructure(['data' => ['field']]);
    }
}
```

