## Factories

Every new model needs a factory in `database/factories/`. The model must `use HasFactory`.

```php
class MyModelFactory extends Factory
{
    public function definition(): array
    {
        return [
            'user_id' => User::factory(),
            'name'    => fake()->word(),
            'status'  => 'active',
        ];
    }

    // Named states for common scenarios
    public function inactive(): static
    {
        return $this->state(['status' => 'inactive']);
    }
}
```

**Bot factory states available**: `active()`, `stopped()`, `withLeverage(int)`.

